OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FEngland fans have said they are
OL,7,Fallowing themselves to be "optimistic
OL,8,Ffor once" ahead of their second World
OL,9,FCup match against Ghana.
OL,11,FThe Three Lions secured a statement 4-
OL,12,F2 win over Croatia in Dallas in their
OL,13,Ftournament opener, leaving many fans
OL,14,Fconfident of the team's chances in the
OL,15,Ftournament.
OL,17,FMore than 14,000 supporters are
OL,18,Fexpected to have travelled to the
OL,19,FMassachusetts' city for the game `
OL,20,Fenduring high ticket costs, transport
OL,21,Fprices and parking charges.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
