OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782181080
OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FThe England faithful were in fine
OL,7,Fvoice on Monday evening in downtown
OL,8,FBoston, with former Three Lions winger
OL,9,FDavid Bentley leading hundreds in a
OL,10,Frendition of Wonderwall by Oasis.
OL,12,FA venue called The Greatest Bar saw a
OL,13,Fsea of red and white shirts chant and
OL,14,Fdance with inflatable unicorns and
OL,15,Fbeachballs as the city's heavy rain
OL,16,Ffailed to dampen England's spirits
OL,17,Fbefore Tuesday's match ` with one fan
OL,18,Feven sporting a mohawk akin to that of
OL,19,FDavid Beckham from the early 2000s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782181080
OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FAt the same event, comic character and
OL,7,FSunday league football manager Steve
OL,8,FBracknall, whose real name is Chris
OL,9,FMcClure, encouraged supporters to join
OL,10,Fin with a chant of "we're on our way"
OL,11,F` alluding to England's potentially
OL,12,Fsuccessful route to the World Cup
OL,13,Ffinal.
OL,15,FOn the eve of England's second game,
OL,16,Ffans said the journey to Boston for
OL,17,Fthe game was worth it despite the high
OL,18,Fprices.
OL,26,@rD@TOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
