OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FRhys Thomas, 31, originally from
OL,7,FBirmingham, who travelled to the city
OL,8,Ffrom Connecticut and is going to the
OL,9,Fmatch with his wife and friends, told
OL,10,FPA: "This is actually the first
OL,11,FEngland game I will have been to.
OL,13,F"I live in the States and now the
OL,14,FWorld Cup is here, so I was just like
OL,15,F'we've got to go'.
OL,17,F"It's never been this close to us,
OL,18,FI've never been this close to the
OL,19,FWorld Cup. I'm excited."
OL,26,@rD@EOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
