OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FHe said tickets cost him 490 dollars
OL,7,F(#370) but admitted he had "heard a
OL,8,Flot worse" from others.
OL,10,F"For four of us, I jumped on it ` it
OL,11,Ftook three times of trying to get
OL,12,Fthrough the lottery ticket system and
OL,13,FI was ready to probably pay thousands
OL,14,Flast second, but luckily we just got
OL,15,Fon it so not too bad," he said.
OL,17,FMr Thomas told PA he was staying two
OL,18,Fmiles from the stadium to help cut
OL,19,Fdown the cost of transport.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@JO]rD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
