PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782181080
OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,F"We could walk down if we need to," he
OL,7,Fsaid.
OL,9,FMr Thomas said he was tempted to go to
OL,10,Fthe final if England made it all the
OL,11,Fway as he lives close to the MetLife
OL,12,FStadium in New Jersey.
OL,14,FHe said: "I don't think we'll be in
OL,15,Fthe final, but if we are, it's going
OL,16,Fto be hard not to try and get tickets."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@cO]vD@JOUxD@gO]
