OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FThe city of Boston played host to the
OL,7,FTartan Army for the first two games of
OL,8,Ftheir World Cup campaign, but England
OL,9,Ffans were unsure whether they could
OL,10,Fmatch Scotland fans' drinking habits.
OL,12,FMeet Boston, a tourism organisation in
OL,13,Fthe city, estimated about 50,000
OL,14,FScotland supporters visited for the
OL,15,Fteam's first two matches.
OL,17,FThey said two popular bars ` The
OL,18,FDubliner and The Haven ` reportedly
OL,19,Fserved more than 300 kegs of Tennent's
OL,20,Fbeer between them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
