SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782181080
OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FMr Parkinson said: "I don't think we
OL,7,Fcan compete with the Scottish on that
OL,8,Ffront."
OL,10,F"The Scots are definitely taking the
OL,11,Fgold medal, but we'll give it a good
OL,12,Fgo," Leigham Stone, 38, from Essex,
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FSome England fans said they felt
OL,16,F"lucky" to have secured tickets for
OL,17,Fthe Ghana game.
OL,26,@nD@TOUpD@GO]rD@AOUtD@DO]xD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
