CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782181080
OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FHelen Bernacki, 38, who is attending
OL,7,Fthe match with her brother Joe
OL,8,FBernacki, 43, and cousin Matty
OL,9,FPeacock, 52, told PA they had planned
OL,10,Fto travel to Boston even if they had
OL,11,Ffailed to secure tickets.
OL,13,FMs Bernacki, who grew up in London,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We've been talking about coming
OL,15,Fout here for a couple of years, saying
OL,16,Fit would be really good to go, and we
OL,17,Fdidn't think we'd get tickets.
OL,19,F"We thought it would still be so great
OL,20,Ffor the atmosphere anyway but we were
OL,21,Flucky enough."
OL,26,@vD@GOU{D@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
