OL,3,CEngland fans allowing themselves to be
OL,4,C'optimistic' ahead of Ghana match
OL,6,FThey said they paid 500 dollars(#377)
OL,7,Feach for a ticket to the game but said
OL,8,Fstaying with a relative in Boston
OL,9,Fmeant they could save money on
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FMr Peacock, from Medway, Kent, said:
OL,13,F"That's why we can afford a ticket."
OL,15,FJoe Bernacki, 43, who now lives in
OL,16,FMassachusetts after living in London,
OL,17,Fsaid: "That sounds relatively cheap to
OL,18,Fwhat I've heard other people have paid
OL,19,F` but still, Jesus."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@dO]yD@GOU{D@TO]
